mcqs.question:
What will be the output of the following code if run with 4 threads?
int sum = 0;
#pragma omp parallel for reduction(+:sum)
for(int i=1; i<=100; i++)
 sum += i;

What is the output of:
int x = 10;
#pragma omp parallel for reduction(max:x)
for(int i=0; i<5; i++)
 x = i;
printf("%d", x);
